<span class="displaytext">(candidate full) made the following statement today regarding president bush's intention to nominate michael mukasey to be the attorney general of the united states: <p>"the president could not have picked a person with greater integrity than michael mukasey to be the next attorney general. as in everything michael does, he will meet and exceed all expectations in his new role. </p><p>"he is a great lawyer with vast experience and during his 18 years on the u.s. district court for the southern district of new york – six serving as chief judge – michael was considered to be one of the best judges in the country." </p><p></p></span>



